TELEM:Aggregator.TELEM:name: spr
TELEM:Aggregator.TELEM:description: Sapphire Rapids PM PMT Telemetry samples definition and transformation rules

TELC:sample.name: LOCAL_REVISION
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Local Revision ID for this product.

TELC:sample.name: XTAL_FREQ
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Represents the clock rate of the XTAL on this silicon.

TELC:sample.name: FET
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Current Frequency Excursion Threshold. It is the ratio of the core frequency. Pcode Clips betwen Pm and P01.

TELC:sample.name: TW
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Unit is 2.3 * power(2, TW) ms and (2^17 ms = ~302 seconds). X is clipped to betwen 0 and 1

TELC:sample.name: OOB_PEM_ENABLE
TELC:sample.TELC:description: 0x0 (Default)=Inband interface for PEM is enabled. 0x1=OOB interface for PEM is enabled.

TELC:sample.name: ANY
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Set if core frequency excursion occurs due to listed or unlisted reason

TELC:sample.name: THERMAL
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Set if core frequency excursion occurs due to thermal event in core/uncore

TELC:sample.name: EXT_PROCHOT
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Set if core frequency excursion occurs due to external prochot assertion

TELC:sample.name: PBM
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Set if core frequency excursion occurs due to power limit (socket and/or platform RAPL)

TELC:sample.name: PL1
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Set if core frequency excursion occurs due to PL1 input from any interface

TELC:sample.name: PL2
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Set if core frequency excursion occurs due to PL2 input from any interface

TELC:sample.name: PMAX
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Set if core frequency excursion occurs due to PMAX

TELC:sample.name: PEM_ANY
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Free running duration counter. Duration for which core frequency excursion occurred due to listed or unlisted reason

TELC:sample.name: PEM_THERMAL
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Free running duration counter. Duration for which core frequency excursion occurred due to EMTTM .

TELC:sample.name: PEM_EXT_PROCHOT
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Free running duration counter. Duration for which core frequency excursion occurred due to external PROCHOT assertion .

TELC:sample.name: PEM_PBM
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Free running duration counter. Duration for which core frequency excursion occurred due to PBM .

TELC:sample.name: PEM_PL1
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Free running duration counter. Duration for which core frequency excursion occurred due to PL1 .

TELC:sample.name: PEM_PL2
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Free running duration counter. Duration for which core frequency excursion occurred due to PL2 .

TELC:sample.name: PEM_PMAX
TELC:sample.TELC:description: Free running duration counter. Duration for which core frequency excursion occurred due to PMAX.
